@startuml 订单拆分与合并流程
!include <C4/C4_Container>

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FEFEFE
    BorderColor #555555
}

' Colors
!define SERVICE_COLOR #E8F5E9
!define ENGINE_COLOR #E3F2FD
!define DB_COLOR #F3E5F5

title 订单拆分与合并 — 原子服务时序

' ========== 拆分流程 ==========

== 阶段 1：订单拆分 ==

actor "流程引擎\n(ProcessEngine)" as ProcessEngine #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "拆单服务\n(OrderSplitService)" as SplitService #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "拆分策略\n(SplitStrategy)" as Strategy #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "状态机引擎\n(StateMachineEngine)" as Engine #ENGINE_COLOR
database "订单DB\n(order)" as OrderDB #DB_COLOR
database "子订单DB\n(sub_order)" as SubOrderDB #DB_COLOR

ProcessEngine -> SplitService: splitOrder(parentOrderId, strategy)
activate SplitService

note right #FEFEFE
  触发时机：流程引擎 Step 0
  策略来源：Apollo process.strategy
  by_warehouse / by_vendor / by_item
end note

SplitService -> Strategy: resolve(parentOrderId)
activate Strategy

Strategy -> Strategy: 按仓库/供应商/品类分组
Strategy --> SplitService: SplitPlan(3 groups)
deactivate Strategy

SplitService -> SplitService: 前置校验
note right #FEFEFE
  • 拆分量 ≤ 5个子订单
  • 所有订单行可拆分
  • 金额分摊验证
end note

loop 为每个拆分组的创建子订单
    SplitService -> Engine: transition(childOrderId, null, PENDING_PAY, ctx)
    activate Engine
    Engine --> SplitService: ✅ PENDING_PAY
    deactivate Engine

    SplitService -> SubOrderDB: INSERT sub_order\n(parentOrderNo, items, amount)
    activate SubOrderDB
    SubOrderDB --> SplitService: ✅
    deactivate SubOrderDB

    note right #FEFEFE
      子订单：
      • 独立 orderNo（id-generator）
      • 继承父订单的 buyer/address
      • 独立状态机实例
      • amount = 分摊后金额
    end note
end

SplitService -> OrderDB: UPDATE parent_order\nstatus=SPLIT_STATUS, child_ids=[...]
activate OrderDB
OrderDB --> SplitService: ✅
deactivate OrderDB

SplitService --> ProcessEngine: ✅ [childOrderNo1, childOrderNo2, ...]
deactivate SplitService

note right #FEFEFE
  父订单标记为已拆分：
  • status 不变（保持 PENDING_PAY）
  • child_order_nos 记录子列表
  • buyer/operator 所见仍是父订单
  • 子订单用于后续独立流转（发货/退款）
end note

' ========== 合并流程 ==========

== 阶段 2：订单合并 ==

actor "XXL-Job\n(定时调度)" as XxlJob #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "合单服务\n(OrderMergeService)" as MergeService #SERVICE_COLOR

XxlJob -> MergeService: mergeOrders(candidateOrderIds)
activate MergeService

note right #FEFEFE
  触发：XXL-Job 每 30 分钟
  条件：同一买家 + 同一店铺
        + 状态均为 PAID
        + 目标订单可合并
  策略：by_vendor（同店合并）
        no_merge（不合并）
end note

MergeService -> MergeService: 前置校验
note right #FEFEFE
  • 所有订单状态 = PAID
  • 相同 buyer_id
  • 相同 shop_id
  • 合并后金额校验
end note

MergeService -> MergeService: 选定目标订单（最早创建的）
MergeService -> OrderDB: 合并订单行到目标订单
activate OrderDB
OrderDB --> MergeService: ✅
deactivate OrderDB

loop 关闭源订单（除目标订单外）
    MergeService -> Engine: transition(sourceOrder, PAID, CANCELLED, '合并')
    activate Engine
    Engine --> MergeService: ✅ CANCELLED
    deactivate Engine

    MergeService -> OrderDB: UPDATE source_order\nmerge_to=targetOrderNo
    activate OrderDB
    OrderDB --> MergeService: ✅
    deactivate OrderDB
end

MergeService -> OrderDB: UPDATE target_order\nmerge_from=[sources], adjust_freight
activate OrderDB
OrderDB --> MergeService: ✅
deactivate OrderDB

note right #FEFEFE
  合并后：
  • 目标订单：状态保持 PAID
  • 源订单：标记为 CANCELLED + merge_to
  • 运费：重新计算（合并运费减免）
  • buyer 查询仅看到目标订单
end note

MergeService --> XxlJob: ✅ mergedCount=2
deactivate MergeService

@enduml
